hands_on_practices.solution:
相关方程：
1. 弗里德曼方程：
$$H^2 \approx \frac{V(\phi)}{3M_p^2}\,,\quad V(\phi)=\lambda\phi^p.$$
2. 克莱因-戈登方程（慢滚）：
$$3H\dot\phi\approx -V'(\phi)=-\lambda p\,\phi^{p-1}.$$
3. 每个哈勃时间内的经典滚动：
$$\Delta\phi_{cl}\approx\frac{|\dot\phi|}{H}
=\frac{|V'|}{3H^2}
=\frac{\lambda p\,\phi^{p-1}}{3\,(\lambda\phi^p/(3M_p^2))}
=p\,\frac{M_p^2}{\phi}\,. $$
4. 量子涨落：
$$\delta\phi\approx\frac{H}{2\pi}
=\frac{1}{2\pi}\sqrt{\frac{\lambda\phi^p}{3M_p^2}}\,. $$
在 $\phi=\phi_*$ 处令两者相等：
$$p\,\frac{M_p^2}{\phi_*}
=\frac{1}{2\pi}\sqrt{\frac{\lambda\phi_*^p}{3M_p^2}}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\phi_*^{p+2}
=12\pi^2\,p^2\,\frac{M_p^6}{\lambda}\,. $$

5. 暴胀结束：$\epsilon(\phi_{end})=1$ 且
$$\epsilon=\frac{M_p^2}{2}\Bigl(\frac{V'}{V}\Bigr)^2
=\frac{M_p^2p^2}{2\phi^2}\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\phi_{end}^2=\frac{p^2M_p^2}{2}\,. $$

6. 从 $\phi$ 到 $\phi_{end}$ 的e-折叠数：
$$N(\phi)=\int_{\phi_{end}}^{\phi}\frac{V}{M_p^2|V'|}d\phi
=\int_{\phi_{end}}^{\phi}\frac{\phi}{pM_p^2}\,d\phi
=\frac{\phi^2-\phi_{end}^2}{2pM_p^2}\,. $$

7. 在 $\phi_{pivot}$ 处的CMB归一化：
$$\mathcal{P_s}
=\frac{V^3}{12\pi^2M_p^6(V')^2}
=\frac{\lambda\phi_{pivot}^{p+2}}{12\pi^2p^2M_p^6}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\lambda
=\frac{12\pi^2p^2M_p^6\,\mathcal{P_s}}{\phi_{pivot}^{p+2}}\,. $$

组合以求 $\phi_*$：
$$\phi_*^{p+2}
=\frac{12\pi^2p^2M_p^6}{\lambda}
=\frac{\phi_{pivot}^{p+2}}{\mathcal{P_s}}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\phi_*^2
=\phi_{pivot}^2\,\mathcal{P_s}^{-\frac{2}{p+2}}\,. $$

通过 $N_{pivot}$ 表示 $\phi_{pivot}^2$：
$$N_{pivot}
=\frac{\phi_{pivot}^2-\phi_{end}^2}{2pM_p^2}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\phi_{pivot}^2
=2pM_p^2\,N_{pivot}+\frac{p^2M_p^2}{2}\,. $$

因此
$$\phi_*^2
=\Bigl(2pN_{pivot}+\tfrac{p^2}{2}\Bigr)M_p^2\,
\mathcal{P_s}^{-\frac{2}{p+2}}\,. $$

最后
$$N_*
=\frac{\phi_*^2-\phi_{end}^2}{2pM_p^2}
=\frac{\bigl(2pN_{pivot}+\tfrac{p^2}{2}\bigr)\mathcal{P_s}^{-\frac{2}{p+2}}
-\tfrac{p^2}{2}}{2p}
=\Bigl(N_{pivot}+\tfrac{p}{4}\Bigr)\mathcal{P_s}^{-\frac{2}{p+2}}
-\frac{p}{4}\,. $$
